{"tid":33124,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"反共大將軍渡邊麻友會有乜下場？","createTime":"2016-12-10T15:20:26.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T15:31:54.000Z","uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"169ed0adb81178a3cdbdf3db8d35bdcc773249b3","tid":33124,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T15:20:26.000Z","msg":"【中國不歡迎你】AKB48上海騷遭反日人士抗議 粉絲反擊 搶中國國旗丟入垃圾桶 <br />\n<br />\n 日本女子偶像組合AKB48派出三名成員渡邊麻友、川本紗矢同伊豆田莉奈現身上海舉行&amp;#22021;活動，宣佈組合&amp;#22175;緊&amp;#21946;中國&amp;#22021;發展大計。<br />\n<br />\n現場除&amp;#21655;唔少AKB&amp;#22021;國內粉絲，仲有一班愛國人士踩場，佢&amp;#21707;手執「萬眾一心 愛我中華 抵制日韓」&amp;#22021;字句，仲有人拎住AKB同日本首相安倍晉三&amp;#22021;合照，以及AKB為日本自&amp;#34910;隊拍攝&amp;#22021;宣傳海報。現場&amp;#22021;抗議人士話，「一二．九」抗日救亡運動紀念日&amp;#21873;&amp;#21873;過&amp;#21655;，南京大屠殺紀念日又即將來臨，偏偏&amp;#21946;呢個時候有對中日關係有負面影響&amp;#22021;偶像團體&amp;#22175;到大陸，「實在令人難以接受」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">據報道指，一眾反日抗議人士令在現&amp;#22021;AKB支持者非常不滿，fans激動得扯下橫額，兼用日語罵爆，更將抗議者手中&amp;#22021;大陸國旗丟入垃圾桶。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161210/large/1481363913_04d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161210%2Flarge%2F1481363913_04d9.jpg&h=aecbc48b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161210/large/1481363896_516f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161210%2Flarge%2F1481363896_516f.jpg&h=7e9a5dda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161210/large/1481363897_aedb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161210%2Flarge%2F1481363897_aedb.jpg&h=037a6bc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n反日抗議人士令到現場&amp;#22021;AKB支持者非常不滿，展開衝突。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161210/large/1481363898_214f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161210%2Flarge%2F1481363898_214f.jpg&h=83b16c6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有人將中國國旗丟入垃圾桶。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />麻友友，有無人保護佢"},{"pid":"10d1da3d42947ad3510f36b777bd3ad8c90460f3","tid":33124,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T15:21:25.000Z","msg":"【中國不歡迎你】AKB48上海騷遭反日人士抗議 粉絲反擊 搶中國國旗丟入垃圾桶 <br />\n<br />\n日本女子偶像組合AKB48派出三名成員渡邊麻友、川本紗矢同伊豆田莉奈現身上海舉行嘅活動，宣佈組合嚟緊喺中國嘅發展大計。 <br />\n<br />\n現場除咗唔少AKB嘅國內粉絲，仲有一班愛國人士踩場，佢哋手執「萬眾一心 愛我中華 抵制日韓」嘅字句，仲有人拎住AKB同日本首相安倍晉三嘅合照，以及AKB為日本自衞隊拍攝嘅宣傳海報。現場嘅抗議人士話，「一二．九」抗日救亡運動紀念日啱啱過咗，南京大屠殺紀念日又即將來臨，偏偏喺呢個時候有對中日關係有負面影響嘅偶像團體嚟到大陸，「實在令人難以接受」。 <br />\n<br />\n據報道指，一眾反日抗議人士令在現嘅AKB支持者非常不滿，fans激動得扯下橫額，兼用日語罵爆，更將抗議者手中嘅大陸國旗丟入垃圾桶。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161210/large/1481363913_04d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161210%2Flarge%2F1481363913_04d9.jpg&h=aecbc48b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161210/large/1481363896_516f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161210%2Flarge%2F1481363896_516f.jpg&h=7e9a5dda&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161210/large/1481363897_aedb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161210%2Flarge%2F1481363897_aedb.jpg&h=037a6bc1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n反日抗議人士令到現場嘅AKB支持者非常不滿，展開衝突。 <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161210/large/1481363898_214f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161210%2Flarge%2F1481363898_214f.jpg&h=83b16c6f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n仲有人將中國國旗丟入垃圾桶。"},{"pid":"ab61884f7db4c4527209bc32c097222a08da6cce","tid":33124,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T15:27:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f17734770e9f1e43b3c597aa30ab2ebcc31fe0de","tid":33124,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T15:31:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n保護麻友友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}